            "body": "Hi Reinhard,\u00a0<br /><br />It is actually setup that way, i.e. it shows related articles from the same category that were published most recently. The reason you may be seeing the same 3 is because most of the articles have the category of 'Workplace' assigned to them.\u00a0<br /><br />If you like we can write a script to randomise it further. The only caveat would be that some older articles might display and newer content may not be seen. This isn't a bad thing as long as the content is evergreen. Let me know your thoughts?\u00a0<br /><br />A quick fix would be to add some diversity into the categories and where posts have multiple categories assigned, you could just leave a singular one to produce more specific related articles.\u00a0",
